response.overview: This program collects 10 truly classic short cartoons, featuring early appearances from beloved characters like Daffy Duck, Mutt and Jeff, Molly Moo Cow, Hunky and Spunky, Mighty Mouse, and Porky Pig. Episodes:  Yankee Doodle Daffy (1943)  Molly Moo-Cow and Rip Van Wrinkle (1935)  Gold Rush Daze (1939)  Slick Sleuths (1926, Redrawn)  You Can't Shoe a Horse Fly (1940)  The Lost Dream (1949)  Confusions of a Nutzy Spy (1943)  Wolf! Wolf! (1944)  Robin Hood Makes Good (1939)  Ding Dog Daddy (1942)
response.title: Cartoon Craze Presents: All-Stars Volume 1
